Description:
I'm pleased to offer this beautiful vintage Levenger briefcase/attache.  This briefcase is in like new condition - it honestly does not look like anyone ever used it. Both sides have a zipper starting at the top of the attache and ending at the bottom to allow the attache to lay flat.  When the attache is fully unzipped and laying flat, the main "compartment" has an area for a cell phone, 4 pens/pencils and business cards.  There is also flat slip pocket behind the "cell phone compartment" for holding files, paper, etc.  On the business card side of the attache compartment, there are 3 additional slip pockets for holding files, papers, etc.
